OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC unveils modernised     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fflagship TV news studio    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC has unveiled its upgraded TV   
OL,6, news studio for its flagship           
OL,7, programmes, including the BBC News at  
OL,8, Ten.                                   
OL,10,FThe studio will feature more           
OL,11,Finteractive screens, a robotic camera  
OL,12,Fand a "new giant, curved catwalk".     
OL,14,F"It gives us a platform which allows us
OL,15,Fto tell stories in a much more vibrant,
OL,16,Fcreative and impactful way," said      
OL,17,Fpresenter Huw Edwards.                 
OL,19,FIt will be seen for the first time on  
OL,20,FBBC One's News at Ten on Monday.       
